 } } \right]$$<br><br>$$ \because $$ $${q_{23}} = {{ - k} \over 8} $$
<br><br>$$\Rightarrow {k \over {(20 + 12\alpha )}}( - 3\alpha  - 4) = {{ - k} \over 8} $$
